      • compress

        public SELF compress()
        This method will tell the builder to compress the bytes. The returned writer or stream will contain an appropriate compressor. If the defined target specifies a name with a file ending, the builder will try to use the appropriate compressor for the file extension. If there is no extension or it is unknown this simply adds a DeflaterOutputStream to the chain. If you want to add file extensions to the automatic selection see CompressorRegistry.registerWrapper(java.lang.String, com.github.powerlibraries.io.helper.InputStreamWrapper, com.github.powerlibraries.io.helper.OutputStreamWrapper).
        Returns:
        this builder
